title: Sydney SumSoc Community Volunteer form

embed.description: Welcome Summoners! Are you interested in taking your skills and friendly attitude from the rift to the realm of reality. We are looking for Volunteers for in-person community events in the near future based in the Sydney area.

body:
Hello Summoners, 

Summoners Society has an awesome opportunity for you, if you are currently located in Sydney. We are looking for awesome people to come join our team of volunteers for our live events.

Summoner Society

https://www.facebook.com/groups/SummonersSocietyOCE/
https://www.facebook.com/summonerssociety
@SumSocOce
